N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 10 ยง 790.4 - Withdrawals of applications

State Regulations

An application made to the Public Health Council in
accordance with this Part may, on written request of the applicant, be
withdrawn prior to decision by the council at any time without prejudice to
resubmission. Notes
